gwt.canvas.client.impl
Class CanvasImpl

java.lang.Object
  gwt.canvas.client.impl.CanvasImpl
Direct Known Subclasses:
CanvasImplIE, CanvasImplMozilla, CanvasImplOpera, CanvasImplSafari
public class CanvasImpl
extends java.lang.Object

The default implementation of the canvas widget. (This file has been modified by hao1300@gmail.com to allow for some of the newer features of HTML canvas.)

See Also:
http://www.whatwg.org/specs/web-apps/current-work/#the-canvas, http://www.w3.org/html/wg/html5/#the-canvas, http://canvex.lazyilluminati.com/tests/tests/results.html
